{"tid":85534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 人生一大難題 剝智慧齒","createTime":"2017-01-18T11:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T09:37:36.000Z","uid":50603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b526f461cda639641e1e1beaf933931136d7852","tid":85534,"uid":50603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:39:18.000Z","msg":"下排智慧齒橫生左 要剝 但是照完掃描發現牙腳距離神經線1mm 左右 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牙醫話整到神經線有機會臉癱或影響味覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟普通牙醫處唔處理度 定係去專科比貴一倍有多好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36752ec0f326f433dbacec38c011701cfa37fd2","tid":85534,"uid":50603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:41:14.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"2ba48c4a46806625ea98fb3b7de3ead4d21467b2","tid":85534,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:42:08.000Z","msg":"唔好慳，去專科"},{"pid":"96cf2227f72e73e24c38a0dc243090fafc95c79f","tid":85534,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:43:55.000Z","msg":"普通牙醫都唔會敢幫你啦 幾千都要慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ec1ae44b796c0f3e6f7238f7985611d2f84d68","tid":85534,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:47:32.000Z","msg":"你同我當年個case一撚樣<br />\n我當時係睇一個相熟既普通牙醫<br />\n但佢話係有咁既風險<br />\n問題係個風險係大定小<br />\n佢話佢做十幾年牙醫<br />\n從未整到人面癱<br />\n最後佢幫我拔哂左面上同下既橫生智慧牙<br />\n洗左六千蚊<br />\n<br />\n佢有諗過轉介我去專科<br />\n但佢話專科係拔得快D<br />\n分別不大"},{"pid":"e938f4c77436f507edf424046f5c661fda2bcccd","tid":85534,"uid":50603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:08:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普通牙醫都唔會敢幫你啦 幾千都要慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢就是話可以照做或轉介都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過又講有風險<br />\n<br />\n都差3000蚊架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1411f6d0a3501253f26189a09a8018d208c2ec03","tid":85534,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:09:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>普通牙醫都唔會敢幫你啦 幾千都要慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢就是話可以照做或轉介都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過又講有風險<br />\n<br />\n都差3000蚊架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n安全要緊呀，巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24d036f107bc0270cbb1a22ad999fef56e5a899","tid":85534,"uid":50603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:13:45.000Z","msg":"其實專科有咩差別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去菲臘牙科得唔得呢"},{"pid":"2a7f15b40641d75d87159c98e5e19a7a14d864f1","tid":85534,"uid":50603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實專科有咩差別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去菲臘牙科得唔得呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210e3f391970182e8478c64a726fd7ea2c7cf12b","tid":85534,"uid":55411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你同我當年個case一撚樣<br />\n我當時係睇一個相熟既普通牙醫<br />\n但佢話係有咁既風險<br />\n問題係個風險係大定小<br />\n佢話佢做十幾年牙醫<br />\n從未整到人面癱<br />\n最後佢幫我拔哂左面上同下既橫生智慧牙<br />\n洗左六千蚊<br />\n<br />\n佢有諗過轉介我去專科<br />\n但佢話專科係拔得快D<br />\n分別不大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打睇嗰個牙醫係咪性趙？<br />\n我之前都拔左兩隻，都係六千蚊。<br 